            <h2>About Us</h2>
            <p>FitoStyle is not just a cafe, it is a place where every guest finds not only exquisite taste, but also inspiration for a healthy lifestyle. Made from herbs grown on the beautiful slopes of the Armenian Highlands, our teas, low-caffeine flavored coffees, and a variety of low-sugar baked goods are the perfect combination of taste and benefits for your body.</p>
        </section>
        <section id="text-03" class="side-section">
            <h2>Taste and Wellness</h2>
            <p>We strive to create not only a pleasant entertainment place, but also a center to support a healthy lifestyle. Here you will find not only the pleasure of taste, but also the opportunity to get acquainted with the useful properties of our products, as well as to participate in interesting events and master classes on healthy eating.</p>
